---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Still Us" description="Learn how Still Us handles your personal data and protects your privacy.">
  <Navbar />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-0">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="bg-canvas-deeper py-16 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-label uppercase text-brand mb-3">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl text-white mb-4 tracking-[-0.02em]">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-white/45 text-sm">Last updated: January 1, 2026</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="bg-canvas py-16 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto prose-legal">

        <section>
          <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            Still Us ("we", "us", "our") is a private mobile application designed exclusively
            for couples. We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your data
            with the care it deserves. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect,
            how we use it, and your rights regarding it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>

          <h3>Account Information</h3>
          <p>When you register, we collect:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Display name</li>
            <li>Profile photo (optional)</li>
            <li>Password (stored as a secure hash — never in plain text)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>App Content You Create</h3>
          <p>To provide the app's features, we store the content you create, including:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Tasks and their details</li>
            <li>Calendar events</li>
            <li>Mood updates</li>
            <li>Messages (including time-delayed, time-locked, and password-locked messages)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Your messages are stored securely in Firebase Firestore. Password-locked message
            bodies are never transmitted to other clients — verification happens server-side
            via Firebase Cloud Functions.
          </p>

          <h3>Device Information</h3>
          <p>
            We collect your device's push notification token (FCM token) solely to deliver
            notifications to you. Tokens are refreshed on every app launch.
          </p>

          <h3>Usage Data</h3>
          <p>
            We do not use third-party analytics SDKs. We may collect aggregate, anonymised
            usage statistics through Firebase to monitor app stability.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information only to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide and maintain the Still Us service</li>
            <li>Connect you with your linked partner</li>
            <li>Deliver messages at the scheduled time or after password verification</li>
            <li>Send push notifications you have opted in to receive</li>
            <li>Diagnose and fix technical issues</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We do not sell your data. We do not use your data for advertising. We do not
            share your data with third parties except as described in Section 5.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>4. Data Shared Between Partners</h2>
          <p>
            By design, some data is visible to your linked partner within the app:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your current mood and display name</li>
            <li>Tasks you create or are assigned to</li>
            <li>Calendar events in your shared couple space</li>
            <li>Messages you send to your partner</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Before a couple link is established, no data is shared between users.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>
            Still Us is built on <strong>Google Firebase</strong>, which provides our database,
            authentication, and cloud functions. Your data is stored on Firebase infrastructure
            in accordance with Google's data processing terms. Please review
            <a href="https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Firebase's privacy policy</a>
            for details.
          </p>
          <p>
            We use <strong>Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM)</strong> to deliver push notifications
            via Apple APNs and Google FCM infrastructure.
          </p>
          <p>
            We do not integrate advertising networks, social login SDKs, or third-party
            analytics services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain your data for as long as your account is active. You may request deletion
            of your account and all associated data at any time by contacting us (see Section 9).
            After deletion, data is removed from our live systems within 30 days and from backups
            within 90 days.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Still Us is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect
            personal information from children under 13. If you believe a child under 13
            has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Object to or restrict processing of your data</li>
            <li>Port your data to another service</li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at the address in Section 9.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Still Us</strong><br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@stillus.app">privacy@stillus.app</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of
            significant changes via in-app notification. Continued use of Still Us after
            changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-legal section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .prose-legal h2 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1A1A2E;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .prose-legal h3 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1A1A2E;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .prose-legal p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #6B7280;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }

  .prose-legal ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  .prose-legal li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #6B7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .prose-legal li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #E8547A;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .prose-legal a {
    color: #E8547A;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .prose-legal a:hover {
    color: #C43060;
  }

  .prose-legal strong {
    color: #1A1A2E;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
